# AquaFlow environment variables (Vite exposes only VITE_-prefixed vars to the client)

# Optional — WorldTides API key (https://www.worldtides.info). If unset, the app
# tries the keyless Open-Meteo Marine sea-level endpoint and otherwise falls back
# to a modeled sine tide, clearly labeled "modeled" in the UI.
VITE_WORLDTIDES_KEY=
